title: THURSDAY 1/14 - Divisional Round matchups 2021
itunes:title: THURSDAY 1/14 - Divisional Round matchups 2021
description:
Some great matchups in the Divisional round...two living legends facing off as Tom Brady and Drew Brees (0:06) look to advance to the NFC Championship. Aaron Donald (0:49) and the Rams taking on the Packers and Matt LaFleur knows his team will have its hands full dealing with the Rams defense (1:05). In the AFC The Ravens and Bills (2:07) will do battle, while Patrick Mahomes prepares to face off against Myles Garrett and the Browns (2:34). We have the latest on coaching interviews (3:31) and Ben Roethlisberger's future in Pittsburgh (3:47)
